      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">16/2/80 ¶  ¶ With the ship  ¶ Shannon ¶  I have sent you, noble Friend, 3 cases again, of which the contents it is to be hoped will give you pleasure and arrive safely at your place. Messrs Watson &amp; S...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">80.02.16</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Ferdinand von Krauss</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Staatliches Museum für Naturkunde, Stuttgart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation by Krauss: 'Bitte um Pettard, W. F. a monograph of the Landshells of Tasmania Launceston (Tasmania) 1879 8° (61 s u table) darum gebeten d. 27. Juni 80. Empf. d. 2. April Rep. 27. Juni' [Asked for Pettard, W. F. a monograph of the Landshells of Tasmania Launceston (Tasmania) 1879 8° <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(61 pages and table) 27 June 1880. Received 2 April. Replied 27 June]. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>16/2/80</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit dem Schiffe Shannon habe ich an Sie, edler Freund, wieder 3 Kisten expedirt, deren Inhalt Ihnen hoffentlich Freude machen, u. bei Ihnen sicher anlangen wird. Mess. Watson &amp; Scull, Thames Street, (die Firma Blackith &amp; Co ist caput) und Hr. Dr. Sonder werden die Sendung zu Ihnen von London u. Hamburg vermitteln.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Unter den Reptilien von Nickol-Bay sollte sich doch <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Neues</hi>
               </seg> finden. Je mehr Sie die Untersuchung derselben <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">beeilen, um</hi>
               </seg> so besser wird es sein, denn die Concurrenz in der Zoologie wird selbst hier täglich grösser.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Stets der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Ich habe Anstalt getroffen, den Osteoglossum für Sie zu erlangen.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">16/2/80</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With the ship <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Shannon</seg> I have sent you, noble Friend, 3 cases again, of which the contents it is to be hoped will give you pleasure and arrive safely at your place. Messrs Watson &amp; Scull, Thames Street, (the firm Blackith &amp; Co. is bust) and Dr Sonder will arrange the consignment to you from London and Hamburg.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Among the reptiles from Nickol Bay<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">WA.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">some new things</hi>
               </seg> should surely be found. The more you <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">hasten</hi>
               </seg> the research on them the better it will be, because the competition in zoology is becoming greater here day by day.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I have contacted institutions to get the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Osteoglossum</seg> for you. <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">What follows is on a separate sheet prepared by Carl Groener on M's behalf that probably accompanied M's letter (though it may have travelled with the boxes of specimens). It has annotations: 'Angekommen den 2. Juli 80' [Arrived 2 July 1880] and 'Berichtet hierüber d. 7. Juli 80' [Reported on it 7 July 1880].</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 12 February 1880</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Pr <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">"Shannon”</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">for Stuttgard<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Stuttgart.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">3 cases 1/3</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">D. K. 1</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Stuttgard</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">One case containing</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="Table1">
               <row>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">One large pair of grey Kangooroh<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                           <p rend="Footnote"
                              style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                              xml:lang="en">MS annotation by Krauss 'M giganteus Schw. <seg>♂</seg>
                              <seg>♀</seg>'.</p>
                        </note>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; "
                        rows="3">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 36pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">} </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">One blue Wallaby<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                           <p rend="Footnote"
                              style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                              xml:lang="en">MS annotation by Kraus: 'Wa[…] frenatus Gld'.</p>
                        </note>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">from Victoria</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">One large black Eagle<note xml:id="ftn7" type="footnote" n="7">
                           <p rend="Footnote"
                              style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                              xml:lang="en">MS annotation by Krauss: 'Aquila audax Lath. Schwanzfedern abgespalten' [Tail feathers split].</p>
                        </note>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">One pair of Nestors. New Zealand<note xml:id="ftn8" type="footnote" n="8">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotations by Krauss: 'meridionalis od. nicht mehr schicken, dagegen Nestor notabilis u. productus Gld.' [send no more <seg style="font-style: italic; ">meridionalis</seg> or, on the other hand <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Nestor notabilis</seg> and <seg style="font-style: italic; ">productus </seg>Gould]; and '2 Rhipidura albiscapa Gld.'.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">One parcel of [bool].<note xml:id="ftn9" type="footnote" n="9">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">books? MS annotated by Krauss: '(Bücher)’ [(books)] and ‘unbedeutend' [insignificant].</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">No 2</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">one case containing</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Collection of Native weapons from Albany West Australia list attached<note xml:id="ftn10" type="footnote" n="10">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">List not found.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Birds nests from Victoria could not get the names yet.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">No 3</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">one box containing</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">About 60 reptiles etc from Nicoll Bay <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">West Australia</hi>
               </seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn11" type="footnote" n="11">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation underneath Nicoll Bay by Krauss: 'Nickol Bay unter 20° S. Br.' [Nickol Bay below 20° south latitude].</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>There is a further annotation, as follows:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>der Balg v. <seg>♂</seg> Macrop. giganteus Schw. wurde leider durch den Verpacker am Fersen Haut u. Knochen abgebrochen, weil er für die Kiste zu lang war, auch sind die Vorderfüsse durch Fäulnis stark schadhaft.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>nicht mehr schicken</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Solche grosse Bälge sollten nicht an die Stelle, wo sie aufgeschnitten sind, wieder zugenäht u. der Körper u an die Beine mit Material ganz ausgefuttert werden.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es ist viel besser, nachdem die Haut abgezogen ist, sie ausgespannt vom Maul bis zur Schwanzspitze u. dann überall zu conserviren u. dann im […] trocknen zu lassen. Hierauf legt man sie einfach zusammen, die Haarseite nach innen gekehrt. Dadurch nimmt sie sehr wenig Platz weg u. man hat keine so grossen Kisten nöthig, was viel wohlfeiler im Transport ist.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>nach Rostock gegeben:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1 Nestor meridionalis</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1 Rhipidura albiscapa Gld</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[The skin of the <seg>♂</seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Macropus giganteus </seg>Schw. was unfortunately broken by the packer at the heel skin and bones, because it was too long for the box, also the front feet are severely damaged by putrefaction.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Don't send more</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Such large skins should not be sown up again at the place where they are cut open and the body to the legs should be completely lined with material</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is much better after the skin is removed to have it spread out from jaw to end of tail and then to preserve it everywhere and then dry in the […]. Hereupon it is simply laid together the hair side turned to the inside. Thereby it takes up little space and such large boxes are not necessary, which is much less expensive in transport.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Given to Rostock:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Nestor meridionalis</seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Rhipidura</seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">albiscapa</seg> Gld]]</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
